{"tid":249114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英再度要求梁繼昌退出調查UGL委員會","createTime":"2017-05-19T05:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T12:05:22.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3aba6a8c4df351b918214a2a08d471f681fa6cf","tid":249114,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:32:28.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】行政長官梁振英再度發表網誌，重申梁繼昌不適合擔任調查UGL專責委員會委員。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英在專責委員會開會前再發表網誌，重提梁繼昌今年三月指梁振英收取UGL五千萬元，正接受稅局調查，反映梁繼昌有既定立場、有偏見、定見和成見，不適合繼續擔任委員。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英又指，他與UGL簽訂的離職協議列明「只會在不造成利益衝突的情況下提供相關協助」，這是協議的關鍵部分，因此協議不可能出現利益衝突問題，如果任何人認為條款是偽造，「請站出來」。"},{"pid":"129e4a8b12bc387945627813f8a64c5eca532ad9","tid":249114,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:32:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=221707\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D221707&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=3875edff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D221707&h=ef3d1761\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=221707</a>"},{"pid":"f6475bc179e9c1de7b6aa3140909980e8dbb6520","tid":249114,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:35:02.000Z","msg":"點解咁驚佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440e6edbd14f712be706695bf6d9372c749559b9","tid":249114,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:36:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解咁驚佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個換一個咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8383b78cb7daf9453de8e8532bc4a8204099d699","tid":249114,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:36:35.000Z","msg":"臨走